{
  "chapter": 48,
  "chapter_summary": "布旗门在荆州召开大会，独臂掌门人宣布就任，提出三件大事：效忠布旗、为苏浅雪报恩、向展梦白复仇。展梦白与萧飞雨假扮门人混入，展梦白发现独臂掌门竟是本应死去的杨璇。杨璇当众指认展梦白为杀秦无篆凶手，并以毒暗器杀死仗义执言的夏光平。萧飞雨亮明帝王谷身份护住展梦白，两人被困于\"冲浪拳\"围攻中。危急之际，萍儿夺走白布旗，揭露杨璇杀害展梦白满门、强占自己的罪行。展梦白以秦无篆葬身细节驳倒杨璇谎言，群豪倒向展梦白。杨璇仓皇逃窜，暗器伤人后消失。展梦白与萧飞雨在生死关头互诉衷情，揭示杨璇未死、蓝大先生可能参与阴谋等重大秘密。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位兄弟请起。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啸雨挥风，布旗独尊，本座接掌门户，从此号令八方。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本门从来散处各方，今日本座能眼见本门俊彦之士，共聚一堂，实是不胜之喜，只因本门自今日会后，便将群策群力，和衷共济，再不似昔日那般散漫无力……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以本门兄弟才情武功，若能团结一心，实不难与少林、武当、昆仑、丐帮等名门大派，一争长短。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "夏光平",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "回禀掌门，弟子夏光平有事上禀。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "text": "请说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "夏光平",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "我布旗门立门宗旨，乃是兄弟互助之会，并非要与武林争雄斗胜，流血争杀之门户……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "text": "本座难道就不知道本门立门之宗旨何在，却要夏大侠你来指教？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "夏光平",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "弟子不敢，但……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本门人才济济，为何不能逐鹿江湖，看今日之武林究是谁家天下？反而甘于屈居人下？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "text": "掌门之言有理，本门虽是兄弟互助之会，为何不可争雄武林。夏大哥，你还是坐下吧！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟们既然都拥护本座，本座惟有鞠躬尽瘁，发扬本门门户，秦故掌门……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秦故掌门将本门重担交托于我时，本座也曾在他老人家面前发下重誓，必当尽力做好三件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "哪三件事？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这三件事俱是他老人家临死前交托于我的，第一件便是要我使得本门弟子，能效忠布旗，争雄武林，生死随之。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "效忠布旗，生死随之。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第二件事，乃是要本座率领本门弟兄，替他老人家向一人报恩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "不知他老人家恩人是哪一位高贤前辈？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他老人家那位大恩人，志性高洁，有如天人，乃是君山苏夫人，而苏夫人近日又恰巧有事需人相助。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这正是咱们报恩良机，千万不可失去了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "苏浅雪可知你藏旗之地？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "不知。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那第三件事，最是重要，便是本门弟兄无论是谁，都得为他老人家复仇。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那恶徒是谁？是谁害了他老人家？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展——梦——白。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闻得展梦白侠名极盛，怎会害死秦故掌门？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展梦白此人善恶无常，好事也做，坏事也干了不少，秦故掌门说不定就是被他害死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想那展梦白若是单打独斗，怎会是秦故掌门之敌手，只恨他竞使出奸计，若非本座恰巧赶到，将他惊走，秦故掌门只怕连尸骨都要曝于荒山之中，无人埋葬，此事除了本座之外，还有苏夫人亲眼见到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "夏光平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展大侠曾救了夏某性命，若说他会做出此等卑鄙之事，夏某万万不能相信，各位若是不信展大侠之侠义胸襟，不妨再问问江中柱江大哥，赵山君赵大哥。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "text": "他救了你莫非便不能害别人？此人行事，本是善恶不定，江湖中人俱都知道。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "夏光平",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "这……这……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "text": "但什么？本座莫非还会说谎不成？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_guang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "夏光平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江中柱，赵……山君，你……你们……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁是江中柱，赵山君？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人可曾来了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "门外查点名册之人",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既已来了，为何不站起？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "赵山君",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "弟子赵山君。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江中柱",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "在下便是江中柱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "赵山君，抬起头来，瞧着本座眼睛。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展梦白！这厮便是展梦白！他杀了赵山君，夺下他腰牌，混入这里，弟兄们还不快将他拿下！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本门弟子即速动手，无论生擒活捉，俱是奇功一件，违令者以叛门论罪。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "展梦白，恶徒，还我秦故掌门与赵山君赵大哥的命来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "帝王谷萧飞雨在此，谁敢动手？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "赔命来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_sun_jiu_xi",
      "text": "孙九溪，你还不说话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jiu_xi",
      "speaker_name": "孙九溪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江中柱、赵山君，没……没有死，是他……他们情愿将腰……腰牌……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": "char_sun_jiu_xi",
      "text": "孙九溪，你敢叛教？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "将两人一齐毙了，莫要留下活口。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是蓝大先生什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "蓝大先生四个字，也是你提的么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫要留下活口，莫要留下活口……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "梦白，你心里有什么想不开的事，也莫要想了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "咱们两人反正已要死了，能死在一起，就算是老天爷的恩典，想不通的事，做了鬼难道还想不通么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "我想通了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "想通了更好。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "凭什么住手？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "我和他相识以来，会少离多，你让我两人死前好生说两句话，我两人一起死给你看，否则……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "否则怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "否则我就让他先死，再冲出去杀你十几个门下。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "算你聪明……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "梦白……梦白……梦白……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "真开心，我们竟能同时死在一起。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "你可知道这独……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不要说话，我们就静静坐一下，然后……我想来想去，今日是走不出去的了，反正人生多苦恼，我们能静静地坐在一起死，真是福气，不比那些终日勾心斗角活着的人强得多了么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "这独臂掌门便是杨璇。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "杨……杨璇不是已死了么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "杨璇之死，只是蓝大先生亲口向我说的，我虽未亲眼瞧见，但一直相信了他，哪知……哪知……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "莫……莫非以蓝大先生身份之尊，还会骗你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "知人知面不知心，我今日若非亲眼瞧见杨璇，也绝不信蓝大先生竟会骗我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你……你会不会看错？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "我今日一瞧那独臂人那双眼睛，便觉心寒，起先还只当自己胆子变得小了，怎会一见别人眼神就害怕起来……但……但现在，我已知道原因，只因我始终当他死了，死人的眼睛会瞪着我，我自然害怕，何况……何况这死人又曾三番五次害过我，只害得我……害得我……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "难怪他只瞧你眼睛，便认出了你，若非彼此都将对方刻骨铭心地记着，单瞧眼睛怎认得出人来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "不错，我永远记着他，他自也永远记着我，今日若不是他，别人怎会认出我来？唉，这也是天意。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你真要这样说，我……我也认得出你的……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "我本想不出那白布旗被我藏得那般严密，别人怎会寻着，此刻我也想通了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "可是你曾将白布旗的藏处告诉过杨璇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "我与他结交之后，只当他乃是人中俊杰，也曾想将布旗门交托给他，完了秦老前辈的心愿，那时我本待自己将他带去，并未将藏处说得十分清楚，但他的聪明，实是百年难见，竟从我隐约的口风中，便寻出了白布旗，我方才只当他已死，自想不到取旗的人会是他，想来想去都想不通此中道理，我若知道他未死，只怕早已想出原因了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "但我终是还不敢相信蓝大先生竟会对我说谎，直到我看出那些对你动手的大汉使的乃是蓝天锤独创的冲浪拳。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "冲浪拳？唉，好古怪的名字，好古怪的武功，我今日若非亲身遇着，真难相信世上竟有如此拳法。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "若非蓝天锤曾在无意间向我说过这冲浪拳的来历，我也不知。唉，他既未杀了杨璇，却来骗我，事情就变得更是复杂，说不定连蓝大先生都是和苏浅雪一路的人，那日我在情人箭秘窟中，蓝大先生赶来相救，我本甚是感激，但此刻才知其中又有古怪。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "什么古怪？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "试想那秘窟那般秘密，蓝大先生若非轻车熟路，哪有那么容易寻着，他既是轻车熟路，岂非连他也曾参与情人箭的秘密，说不定他就是真正的首脑，何况那日他早不来救我，迟不来救我，却偏偏在我已九死一生，大功告成时赶来，这岂非太巧了么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "这并非我以小人之心度君子之腹，而是事已至此，不得不如此。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "蓝大先生侠名满天下，豪气震江湖，他若真是如此，那他平日也未免装得太像了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我方才见那杨璇施的乃是唐门暗器，还当他是唐迪门下，如今想来必定是唐迪曾将本门暗器私下传授给苏浅雪，苏浅雪再传给他的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "独臂掌门",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你两人话说完了么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "今日你我两人必须有一个人逃出去，你我两人若是都死在这里，这秘密又将永远埋藏。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 447,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你……你……你要我独自逃出去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你……你好狠心，但……但我离开你还能活着么？这……这莫非你还不知道？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 455,
      "line_end": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "今日你若不逃出去，我死难瞑目。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 459,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好，今日我逃出去，但只要我将这秘密说出之后，立刻就……就陪你去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "你……你何苦如此？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我……我的心你莫非还不知道，你还要问我，你要我活着，才是世上最狠心的人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "既……既是如此，你却要等到将这秘密说给天下武林最强之人后才能去死。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "若非武林第一高手，怎制得住蓝天锤？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好，我答应你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "我引开他们注意之力，你冲出去。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是给你们一柄刀，你两人只怕又要争先。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但此刻有两柄刀，你两便可不差分毫，同时而死了，哈哈，本座对你两人可算体贴。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "杨大哥，你这条左臂是谁斫断的？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "谁……谁是杨大哥？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 513
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "你认出了小弟，小弟难道认不出你么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_er",
      "speaker_name": "萍儿",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "认出又怎样？杨璇，就让他临死前再瞧瞧你的脸。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "好！好，果然是小弟的杨大哥。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你我虽曾兄弟一场，但我为了武林正义，今日也不能不大义灭亲了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本座因公不能顾私，只有割袍断义，自此刻你我恩义断绝。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "好，大哥对小弟诸般厚爱，小弟仍不忘结拜之情，想不到大哥竟先要与小弟割袍断义了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 537,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "休得多说，是你自决，还是要人动手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "小弟只想被大哥亲手杀死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 545,
      "line_end": 547
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你要我亲手杀你，那也容易。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 551,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "留神暗器。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 553,
      "line_end": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "大哥莫非不忍心下手么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 567,
      "line_end": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "是极是极，我不忍心下手。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死丫头，放手。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 573,
      "line_end": 573
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_er",
      "speaker_name": "萍儿",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "她不会放手的，你既已杀了展梦白满门，就不该留下她。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 575,
      "line_end": 577
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": "char_ping_er",
      "text": "你……你疯了，快住口。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 581,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_er",
      "speaker_name": "萍儿",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "你既杀了展梦白满门，鸡犬不留，只是见我生得不错，又将我强占了……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 589,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": "char_ping_er",
      "text": "住口。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 591,
      "line_end": 591
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_er",
      "speaker_name": "萍儿",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "我虽然是清白的身子，但从小长在勾栏，迷人的功夫，学了不知多少，可笑你却将我当做黄花大闺女，竟被我三言两语迷得晕头胀脑，一夕过后，便再也舍不得杀我。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 599,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "布旗门下何在，你们眼见掌门被辱，怎不出手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 603,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_er",
      "speaker_name": "萍儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "布旗在我手，我便是掌门，谁敢动手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 623,
      "line_end": 623
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这布旗我是偷来的，你不是偷来的么？弟兄们！快将这姓杨的抓住！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 625,
      "line_end": 627
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "熊大哥可在么？你拿个主意吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 633,
      "line_end": 635
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊正雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，也得先让夫人说完话之后，是非才有公论。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 641,
      "line_end": 643
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好，你等尽管让她说好了，到时门规处置，莫要后悔。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 649,
      "line_end": 651
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "夏光平之友",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "公论是非的人，莫非也要处以门规不成？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 653,
      "line_end": 655
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_er",
      "speaker_name": "萍儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可知道我为何被你强占身子之后还不肯死，反而用尽柔媚手段来迷惑你，我也知道起初你还是不信，有时给我逃走的机会，有时故意呼呼大睡，却将刀剑放在身旁，但我既不逃走，也不乘机杀你，见你睡了，就替你盖被，见你醉了，就去煮醒酒汤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 661,
      "line_end": 663
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_er",
      "speaker_name": "萍儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道这些举动，你都瞧在眼里，这才相信我是死心爱你，要一辈子跟着你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 665,
      "line_end": 667
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_er",
      "speaker_name": "萍儿",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "告诉你，我这么做。为的只是要等今日，要眼看着你死在我手上。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 669,
      "line_end": 671
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": "char_ping_er",
      "text": "你这贱人虽然胡言乱语，展梦白杀害秦故掌门之仇，还是非报不可。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 675,
      "line_end": 677
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秦老前辈乃是死于情人箭下，展某亲手将他老人家埋葬，那白布旗也是他老人家交托于我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 679,
      "line_end": 681
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁，秦前掌门是我安葬的，兄弟们切莫被他骗了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 683,
      "line_end": 683
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_yang_xuan",
      "text": "既是你葬了秦老前辈，可知他老人家死时穿的是何衣物，那坟墓又在哪里？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 687,
      "line_end": 689
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "这……这在莫干山岭。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 691,
      "line_end": 691
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁，幸好我未曾将秦老前辈葬身之处告诉你，各位若是不信，不妨……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 693,
      "line_end": 693
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_zheng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊正雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我等信了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 695,
      "line_end": 695
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展大侠想来未必说假话。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 697,
      "line_end": 699
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到各位……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 701,
      "line_end": 701
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "杨璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去吧！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 701,
      "line_end": 703
    }
